@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About Us</PageTitle>

<MudContainer Class="mt-16">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true" Align="Align.Center">About Us</MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="mb-4">
        Good Boy Catalogue is your ultimate destination for finding the perfect canine companion for any occasion! We understand that sometimes you need a little extra help from a furry friend, whether it's a cuddle buddy for a cozy night in, a playful pal for a day at the park, or a skilled sniffer to find your lost keys. That's why we've created a unique service where you can rent dogs with specialized talents to meet your specific needs.
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="mb-4">
        Our dogs are more than just pets; they're highly trained professionals with unique skills and personalities. Need someone to shred your old pillows? Chompy the Pillow Shredder is your guy! Feeling down and need a hug? Dr. Woof, the Canine Therapist, is here to lend an ear (and a paw). Whatever your need, we have a dog to match.
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="mb-4">
        At Good Boy Catalogue, we're passionate about connecting people with the perfect canine companion. We believe that dogs have the power to enrich our lives in countless ways, and we're committed to making that experience accessible to everyone. So browse our catalog, find your perfect match, and get ready for some tail-wagging fun!
    </MudText>

    <MudDivider Class="my-8" />

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Our Mission:</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="mb-4">
        To provide a convenient and affordable way for people to experience the joy and benefits of dog companionship, while also providing a loving and supportive environment for our canine professionals.
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Our Values:</MudText>
    <MudList T="string">
        <MudListItem Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Pets">Dog Welfare: The well-being of our dogs is our top priority. We ensure they receive the best care, training, and enrichment.</MudListItem>
        <MudListItem Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.SentimentSatisfiedAlt">Customer Satisfaction: We strive to provide exceptional customer service and ensure our clients have a positive experience.</MudListItem>
        <MudListItem Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Groups">Community: We aim to build a strong community of dog lovers and promote responsible dog ownership.</MudListItem>
        <MudListItem Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Lightbulb">Innovation: We're constantly exploring new ways to improve our services and meet the evolving needs of our clients.</MudListItem>
    </MudList>

    <MudDivider Class="my-8" />

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Our Team:</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="mb-4">
        We're a team of passionate dog lovers dedicated to providing the best possible service to our clients and canine companions. Our team includes experienced dog trainers, groomers, and handlers who are committed to ensuring the happiness and well-being of our dogs.
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Contact Us:</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="mb-4">
        Have questions or need help finding the perfect dog? We'd love to hear from you! Contact us at <a href="mailto:[email protected]">[email protected]</a> or call us at [phone number].
    </MudText>
</MudContainer>